<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span style="color:#008000">(صلاصل الزَّيْت إِلَى الشطور ... )</span><a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>